T02TD2715E:81b-1: aa ra pa tsa na s'a dha nam //
T02TD2715E:81b-3: aa ra pa tsa na'i sgrub thabs //
T02TD2715E:81b-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2715E:81b-5: dkar po ri bong 'dzin pa dang 'dra glegs bam ral gris phyag mtshan zhing //
T02TD2715E:81b-6: legs par mdzes pa'i gzhon nu zur phud lnga pa shin tu zhi ba can //
T02TD2715E:81b-7: dga' ba rab rgyas thar pa'i mchog ster padma'i 'dab ma yangs pa'i spyan //
T02TD2715E:81b-8: ngan pa'i blo gros bsreg pa la mkhas 'jam pa'i dbyangs la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2715E:81b-9: skye bo gang dag rnams kyis aa ra pa tsa na yi dngos grub phyir //
T02TD2715E:81b-10: lo phyed bar du rgyun mi 'chad par sbyor ba bsgom pa gang yin pa //
T02TD2715E:81b-11: mchog gi blo dang khyad par byang chub go 'phang nges par 'thob ldan pa'i //
T02TD2715E:81b-12: 'khor lo rin po che yi man ngag shin tu bsdus pa bgyi ba lags //
T02TD2715E:81b-13: dri zhim me tog gcal du bkram zhing dri yi chu yis chags chag btab //
T02TD2715E:81b-14: mnyam zhing gtsang ma sngags rig yid du 'ong ba'i sa yi cha dag tu //
T02TD2715E:81b-15: yid 'ong 'jam pa'i stan ni ci yang rung ba dag la nyer 'dug nas //
T02TD2715E:81b-16: bde bar shin tu mtshan ma med pa'i byang chub sems ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD2715E:81b-17: dngos don don dang bcas pa ma lus kun nas ni //
T02TD2715E:81b-18: stong par rnam par bsgom bya slar yang bdag gi lus //
T02TD2715E:81b-19: de dang de ni 'od gsal nyid du bltas byas la //
T02TD2715E:81b-20: sva bh'a wa shuddha'i gsang sngags yang dag brjod par bya //
T02TD2715E:81b-21: de nas rang snying dang po'i dbyangs las bar snang du //
T02TD2715E:81b-22: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor 'od bzang ldan pa bsgom par bya //
T02TD2715E:81b-23: de nas 'dir ni dh'i:yig du brjod dkar po ste //
T02TD2715E:81b-24: de ni lhag par dri med 'jam pa'i dbyangs su bsam //
T02TD2715E:81b-25: zla ba bye ba dag dang mtshungs pa'i mdangs 'dzin cing //
T02TD2715E:81b-26: kun nas 'bar ba'i rgyan rnams kyis ni spras pa ste //
T02TD2715E:81b-27: chags dang bcas par cung zad 'dzum zhing yid 'phrogs pa //
T02TD2715E:81b-28: padma'i steng na gcig tu bsam gtan des pas bzhugs //
T02TD2715E:81b-29: rang gi snying gar aa yig mchog las 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa yi gzugs //
T02TD2715E:82a-1: med 'od zer dra ba can ni yang dag bsam //
T02TD2715E:82a-2: de yi steng du zla ba'i gzugs brnyan dag la sngags pas bsgom bya ste //
T02TD2715E:82a-3: de ni ri bong 'dzin pa lta bu'i bla ma 'jam dpal dbyangs nyid do //
T02TD2715E:82a-4: g-yas su mdzes pa'i gzugs ldan skra can ma ni rnam par 'dzum pa dang //
T02TD2715E:82a-5: shin tu rgyas pa'i nu ma zung ldan zur gyis de las blta ba ste //
T02TD2715E:82a-6: shin tu mdzes shing sgeg pa'i lus la nye ba'i skra can g-yon logs su //
T02TD2715E:82a-7: mtha' dag yon tan gter du gyur pa tsa na dag las bsgom par bya //
T02TD2715E:82a-8: dri med legs par dkar ba dra ba can gyi 'od //
T02TD2715E:82a-9: re pha las byung mdun du nges par bsam pa nyid //
T02TD2715E:82a-10: 'od kyi rang bzhin yid 'phrog zla ba'i 'od can ni //
T02TD2715E:82a-11: pa yi yi ge las skyes rgyab tu gzhag par bya //
T02TD2715E:82a-12: yang na yi ge bkod pa'i 'od zer 'bar ba yi //
T02TD2715E:82a-13: rgya cher rab tu snang ba nges pas rnam bsgom bya //
T02TD2715E:82a-14: des ni mi shes ri bo 'joms par 'gyur ba dang /
T02TD2715E:82a-15: yid ni rnyog pa med pa'i ye shes dam par byed //
T02TD2715E:82a-16: gti mug mun nag kun nas rnam par 'joms pa yi //
T02TD2715E:82a-17: zla ba'i gzugs brnyan dang 'dra 'od zer dra ba can //
T02TD2715E:82a-18: 'og gi 'khor lo myur du 'khor bar bsam bya zhing //
T02TD2715E:82a-19: lha de rnams ni g-yo ba med pa nyid du blta //
T02TD2715E:82a-20: ri bong can lta'i 'od zer sprin ni rgya chen po//
T02TD2715E:82a-21: phyung nas phyogs bcu po rnams gsal bar gyur pa yis //
T02TD2715E:82a-22: rang lus bzhin du sems can rnams ni brgyan byas te //
T02TD2715E:82a-23: slar yang 'ongs pa snying ga'i zla ba la gzhug bya //
T02TD2715E:82a-24: sngags pas gsang sngags dam pa aa ra pa tsa na ni legs zlos shing //
T02TD2715E:82a-25: brtan pa'i blo yis man ngag bsgoms las blo ngan sdug bsngal rab bcom ste //
T02TD2715E:82a-26: yid kyi shes pa dri med dag dang pha rol phyin pa rnams dang yang //
T02TD2715E:82a-27: mchog tu gyur pa'i sa rnams dang ni gang des rgyal ba thob par 'gyur //
T02TD2715E:82a-28: dam pa'i chos kyi mdzod gyur bla ma dam pa dga' mchog rdo rje yis //
T02TD2715E:82a-29: bde gshegs tshogs kyi spyan sngar cho gas gang zhig mngon par dbang bskur ba //
T02TD2715E:82a-30: blo bzang mi pham bshes gnyen des ni skye bos blo mchog grub bya'i phyir //
T02TD2715E:82a-31: aa ra pa tsa na yi 'khor lo gzhung du yang dag sbyar ba yin //
T02TD2715E:82a-32: 'khor lo'i cho ga bzang po gzhung mchog tu sbyar bas //
T02TD2715E:82a-33: bsod nams rgya chen kun nas bdag gis thob gyur pa //
T02TD2715E:82b-0: gang yin des ni @82b 'jig rten nyon mongs las rgyal zhing //
T02TD2715E:82b-1: nges pa'i bde ba gcig pu 'jam pa'i dbyangs gyur cig //
T02TD2715E:82b-2: aa ra pa tsa na'i sgrub thabs slob dpon chen po mi pham bshes gnyen gyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2715E:82b-4: // / lhag pa'i lha 'di nyid kyis mngon sum du byin gyis brlabs pa'i pandi ta chen po shr'i ba na ratna'i zhal snga nas kyi bka' drin las /
T02TD2715E:82b-5: legs par sbyar ba'i skad gyi cha shas rig pa dge slong rgya mtsho'i sdes 'gyur rnying las cung zad bcos shing //
T02TD2715E:82b-6: rgya dpe'i rkang pa dang mthun par //
T02TD2715E:82b-7: dpal gnod gnas kyi gtsug lag chen por bsgyur ba'o//
